<L>__{interior den}
<A>__{james irish whiskey in one hand, the pride of humboldt county in the other watches with deep absorption as judy and mickey have a heartfelt conversation. then, sensing something ...he turns. hank and irene winters, grocery bags in arm, stand frozen.}
