<D>__{it's no arsonist's daughter, but i guess you know that. it's a young man's book. it got me remembering how it felt to be young.}
<C>__{grady}
<D>__{maybe i should read it.}
<C>__{hank}
<D>__{oh, i don't think there's any danger of you aging prematurely, grady.}
<A>__{grady doesn't have to read hank's face this time.}
